knowledgeGraph.title: Medical City Dallas Hospital
knowledgeGraph.description: Medical City Dallas is a hospital located at 7777 Forest Lane, just west of North Central Expressway, in north Dallas, Texas, United States. It is operated by Hospital Corporation of America.
